            ; Minted at the orchestrating altitude while the stones were being
            ; placed, on the DeepSeek-V4-Flash question that opened the day: a
            ; 91 GB MXFP4/MXFP8/IQ2_XXS GGUF the body cannot read. Q4_K/Q6_K
            ; carry scale INSIDE the superblock -- wl-q6k-d reads the f16 d at
            ; offset 208 of its own 210-byte block, so a block is
            ; self-describing. MXFP4 does not: one 8-bit exponent is shared
            ; across a 32-element group, held apart from the elements. The
            ; teaching is why that makes MXFP4 a new RECIPE and not a new
            ; constant -- self-carried scale is a property of the recipe's
            ; SHAPE, not of its arithmetic, so moving where the scale lives
            ; changes which recipe can hold the number at all.
            ; (walk: equireach at 807 -- both name a cost the recipes assumed
            ; away; that one assumed reach uniform, this one assumed scale
